    text: "Art Safari, the famous art exhibition in the capital of Romania, has reached its tenth edition. After visiting the ninth edition, about which you can find out more information here we set out to reach in the next editions or at least to try. So last weekend we went to Art Safari housed in the Dacia-România Palace in Lipscani street.",
