    text: "I felt I had to dedicate an entirely separate article to one of the accommodations we had in Santorini because it was the most beautiful accommodation we have ever stayed in, and it was an experience in itself. We booked through booking.com and we were so happy that we found this place in the peak season at a reasonable price.",
